                    disponible para proyectos freelance y colaboraciones
                    emocionantes.
                </p>

                <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                    <a
                        href="mailto:hello@axel.dev"
                        class="flex items-center gap-4 group w-max"
                    >
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-surface-hover border border-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-primary transition-transform group-hover:scale-110 shadow-sm"
                        >
                            <iconify-icon
                                icon="solar:letter-linear"
                                class="text-xl"></iconify-icon>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <p class="text-sm text-muted font-medium mb-0.5">
                                Email
                            </p>
